sql:
SELECT COUNT(*) 
FROM stock_prices 
WHERE close > (SELECT AVG(close) FROM stock_prices);

external_knowledge:
- The period of interest is from January 1, 2020, to December 31, 2022;
- The query prioritizes stocks with higher access counts and, in case of a tie, those with more news articles;
- Accesses and news articles are considered indicators of interest and relevance in the stock market.
